Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.30,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}如牵挂般萦绕身旁
Comment: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:24.75,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:27.83,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}能否听到我的呐喊
